---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="mt-32 border-t border-[color:var(--color-border-soft)] bg-[color:var(--color-ink)]/60">
  <div class="container-app py-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
      <div>
        <div class="heading text-sm font-semibold text-[color:var(--color-text)]">
          dux &middot; <span class="text-[color:var(--color-dim)]">pronounced "dooks"</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-[color:var(--color-dim)]">
          MIT licensed. Built by <a class="text-[color:var(--color-muted)] hover:text-[color:var(--color-accent)]" href="https://github.com/patrickdappollonio">@patrickdappollonio</a>.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-[color:var(--color-dim)]">
          Logo (the duck icon) by Chantelle Graham.
        </p>
      </div>
      <nav class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-5 gap-y-2 text-xs">
        <a class="text-[color:var(--color-muted)] hover:text-[color:var(--color-accent)]" href="/docs">Docs</a>
        <a class="text-[color:var(--color-muted)] hover:text-[color:var(--color-accent)]" href="https://github.com/patrickdappollonio/dux">GitHub</a>
        <a class="text-[color:var(--color-muted)] hover:text-[color:var(--color-accent)]" href="https://github.com/patrickdappollonio/dux/releases">Releases</a>
        <a class="text-[color:var(--color-muted)] hover:text-[color:var(--color-accent)]" href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/@patrickdappollonio/dux">npm</a>
        <a class="text-[color:var(--color-muted)] hover:text-[color:var(--color-accent)]" href="https://github.com/patrickdappollonio/dux/issues">Issues</a>
        <a class="text-[color:var(--color-muted)] hover:text-[color:var(--color-accent)]" href="/install.sh">install.sh</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-2 text-[11px] text-[color:var(--color-dim)] sm:flex-row sm:justify-between">
      <span>© {year} <a class="text-[color:var(--color-muted)] hover:text-[color:var(--color-accent)]" href="https://www.patrickdap.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Patrick D'appollonio</a>. No telemetry, no JSON-RPC, no nonsense.</span>
      <span class="mono">curl -sSfL getdux.app/install.sh | bash</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
